22
00:03:17,067 --> 00:03:20,616
<font color="gray">- Er... Can you give us a lift to London?</font>
<font color="gray">- Yes, I suppose so.</font>
- 呃, 你能捎我们去伦敦吗?   - 行, 我觉得可以

23
00:03:20,707 --> 00:03:22,026
<font color="gray">DOCTOR: In you get.</font>
你们进去

24
00:03:23,387 --> 00:03:25,662
<font color="gray">Thank you. Thank you very much.</font>
谢谢你, 非常感谢

25
00:03:37,667 --> 00:03:40,539
<font color="gray">- DOCTOR: Here we are.  - Right</font>
- 我们到啦  - 对了

26
00:03:42,307 --> 00:03:44,822
<font color="gray">Well, that's odd! It says ''Watkins''.</font>
诶, 很奇怪, 上面写的 "Watkins"

27
00:03:44,907 --> 00:03:46,122
<font color="gray">(JAMIE) Must have the wrong house.</font>
肯定搞错房子了

28
00:03:46,207 --> 00:03:49,377
<font color="gray">Well, the telephone directory</font>
<font color="gray">definitely said number 1 8.</font>
啊, 电话号码簿上绝对写的是 18 号啊

29
00:03:49,467 --> 00:03:50,786
<font color="gray">We'll ask.</font>
我们问问

30
00:04:11,027 --> 00:04:12,745
<font color="gray">(DOORBELL RINGING INCESSANTLY)</font>

31
00:04:20,227 --> 00:04:22,900
<font color="gray">If you don't mind, I'm trying to work!</font>
不介意的话, 我还要工作呢!

32
00:04:23,667 --> 00:04:28,263
<font color="gray">Oh. I'm sorry, miss, but we wondered</font>
<font color="gray">whether you could help us.</font>
噢, 抱歉, 小姐. 但我们想问问你能否帮助我们

33
00:04:28,587 --> 00:04:29,736
<font color="gray">We wondered if...</font>
我们想知道...

34
00:04:29,827 --> 00:04:32,546
<font color="gray">Oh, look, now the stupid thing's gone and jammed!</font>
噢, 看, 这个蠢东西又卡住了

35
00:04:32,627 --> 00:04:34,697
<font color="gray">Oh, dear, perhaps I could help you.</font>
噢, 亲爱的, 也许我可以帮你

36
00:04:34,787 --> 00:04:36,220
<font color="gray">Well, do you know anything about cameras?</font>
哦, 你还懂一点相机?

37
00:04:36,307 --> 00:04:38,343
<font color="gray">Yes, a little. I see...</font>
是的, 一点点. 我知道了...

38
00:04:38,427 --> 00:04:39,985
<font color="gray">Now I had it on automatic shutter.</font>
现在我调到了自动快门模式

39
00:04:40,067 --> 00:04:41,625
<font color="gray">Taking photos of yourself?</font>
在自拍呢?

40
00:04:41,707 --> 00:04:44,460
<font color="gray">Yes, then you interrupted me</font>
<font color="gray">and the stupid thing jammed!</font>
是的, 然后你们打断了我, 这个破玩意儿就卡住了

41
00:04:44,547 --> 00:04:46,857
<font color="gray">Have you come to see my uncle?</font>
<font color="gray">He's not here.</font>
你们是来找我叔叔的吧? 他现在不在这里

42
00:04:46,947 --> 00:04:49,505
<font color="gray">But who are you?</font>
<font color="gray">Friends of his? Fellow nuts?</font>
但你们是谁? 他的朋友? 也是技术迷?

43
00:04:49,587 --> 00:04:51,737
<font color="gray">Please let me answer one question at a time.</font>
且让我一个个地回答

44
00:04:51,827 --> 00:04:53,738
<font color="gray">Hey, you be careful with that thing.</font>
<font color="gray">It cost me a fortune.</font>
嘿, 你小心弄这个东西, 它花了我不少钱

45
00:04:53,827 --> 00:04:56,387
<font color="gray">It's all right. It's a very simple mechanism.</font>
没事的, 非常简单的机制

46
00:04:56,467 --> 00:04:58,776
<font color="gray">- Who is your uncle?  - Professor Watkins.</font>
- 你叔叔是谁?   - Watkins 教授

47
00:04:58,867 --> 00:04:59,902
<font color="gray">Oh.</font>
哦

48
00:04:59,987 --> 00:05:02,023
<font color="gray">Then Professor Travers doesn't live here?</font>
那 Travers 教授不住在这里?

49
00:05:02,107 --> 00:05:04,223
<font color="gray">Well, he did. He left about a month ago.</font>
哦, 以前是. 他大概一个月前离开了

50
00:05:04,307 --> 00:05:05,581
<font color="gray">Gone to America for a year with his daughter.</font>
跟他女儿一起去非洲待一年

51
00:05:05,667 --> 00:05:07,066
<font color="gray">Oh, that's just great!</font>
噢, 那太棒了!

52
00:05:07,147 --> 00:05:08,819
<font color="gray">My uncle worked at the Cavendish lab.</font>
我叔叔在 Cavendish 实验室工作

53
00:05:08,907 --> 00:05:10,545
<font color="gray">He wanted to do some work so Professor Travers said</font>
他想做点工作, 于是 Travers 教授说

54
00:05:10,627 --> 00:05:12,538
<font color="gray">he could use his daughter's lab here.</font>
他可以用他女儿的这个实验室

55
00:05:12,627 --> 00:05:15,061
<font color="gray">And I moved in because I got kicked</font>
<font color="gray">out of my studio last week.</font>
而我搬进来是因为我上周被踢出我的工作室了

56
00:05:15,147 --> 00:05:17,422
<font color="gray">What field of science is your uncle in?</font>
你叔叔研究的是哪个领域?

57
00:05:17,507 --> 00:05:20,863
<font color="gray">Oh, I don't know,</font>
<font color="gray">he's in applied physics or something.</font>
哦, 我不知道. 他是搞应用物理什么的吧

58
00:05:20,947 --> 00:05:23,222
<font color="gray">Always messing around with computers</font>
<font color="gray">and things. Complete nut.</font>
总是在摆弄电脑这些. 完全的疯子

59
00:05:23,307 --> 00:05:25,741
<font color="gray">Well, that is fortunate.</font>
<font color="gray">Perhaps he might be able to help us.</font>
哦, 那很幸运啊, 也许他可以帮助我们

60
00:05:25,827 --> 00:05:27,226
<font color="gray">- Is he at home?  - No.</font>
- 他在家吗?   - 不在

61
00:05:27,307 --> 00:05:30,140
<font color="gray">- Well, where is he?</font>
<font color="gray">- Well, how do I know? I'm not his keeper.</font>
- 那, 他在哪儿?   - 哦, 我怎么知道? 我不是他的管家

62
00:05:30,227 --> 00:05:33,219
<font color="gray">- Hey, have you fixed it?</font>
<font color="gray">- Oh, yes, that's all right.</font>
- 嘿, 你修好了吗?   - 哦, 是的, 没事了

63
00:05:33,307 --> 00:05:35,616
<font color="gray">- That's really great, thanks!  - Miss...</font>
- 真是太好了, 谢谢!   - 小姐...

64
00:05:35,707 --> 00:05:36,776
<font color="gray">Hey!</font>
嘿!

65
00:05:37,147 --> 00:05:40,901
<font color="gray">That's a jolly outfit.</font>
<font color="gray">Would you mind posing for me?</font>
这真是件漂亮的衣服. 你介意摆个姿势给我吗?

66
00:05:40,987 --> 00:05:42,136
<font color="gray">- What?  - Look. Just stand there.</font>
- 什么?   - 喏, 就站那里

67
00:05:42,227 --> 00:05:43,899
<font color="gray">- Miss!  - Isobel.</font>
- 小姐!   - 我叫 Isobel

68
00:05:43,987 --> 00:05:47,138
<font color="gray">Yeah, okay. Now just stand here.</font>
<font color="gray">Now get... Head over the shoulder.</font>
对, 好. 就站在那里. 现在...把头朝肩膀过去一点

69
00:05:47,587 --> 00:05:50,021
<font color="gray">Have you any idea</font>
<font color="gray">when your uncle is going to be back?</font>
知道你叔叔什么时候回来吗?

70
00:05:50,107 --> 00:05:52,496
<font color="gray">No, he left about a week ago.</font>
<font color="gray">I haven't seen him since.</font>
不, 他大概一周前走的, 从那之后我就没见过他

71
00:05:52,587 --> 00:05:53,622
<font color="gray">A week?</font>
一周?

72
00:05:53,707 --> 00:05:56,380
<font color="gray">Yeah, he was prattling on about some</font>
<font color="gray">new invention, or something or other,</font>
是, 他一直在叨叨什么新发明, 不知道是什么东西

73
00:05:56,467 --> 00:05:59,027
<font color="gray">and having the chance to develop it.</font>
<font color="gray">Now... Not you.</font>
说有机会来研究它了. 现在...不是你

74
00:05:59,107 --> 00:06:00,699
<font color="gray">- Oh.  - ISOBEL: Okay. Now.</font>
- 噢  - 好, 现在

75
00:06:00,787 --> 00:06:03,096
<font color="gray">Can't you get in touch with him?</font>
你能联系上他吗?

76
00:06:03,227 --> 00:06:04,546
<font color="gray">No, I tried.</font>
不能, 我试过

77
00:06:04,627 --> 00:06:06,697
<font color="gray">I wanted to borrow a couple of quid</font>
<font color="gray">off him in a hurry,</font>
我想找他借几镑救救急

78
00:06:06,787 --> 00:06:08,743
<font color="gray">but, well, they said</font>
<font color="gray">he wasn't available for phone calls.</font>
但是, 他们说他没法接电话

79
00:06:08,827 --> 00:06:10,579
<font color="gray">They! Now... Now who is ''they''?</font>
他们! 说说..."他们"是谁?

80
00:06:10,667 --> 00:06:12,305
<font color="gray">Just get that, will you? I don't know.</font>
拿着这个, 好吗? 我不知道

81
00:06:12,387 --> 00:06:15,060
<font color="gray">International Electric, something or other.</font>
好像是叫＂国际电子＂, 好像是吧

82
00:06:15,147 --> 00:06:16,865
<font color="gray">International Electromatics?</font>
国际电气自动化公司?

83
00:06:16,947 --> 00:06:18,460
<font color="gray">Yes, probably.</font>
是, 像是

84
00:06:19,387 --> 00:06:22,106
<font color="gray">You mean your uncle has gone to</font>
<font color="gray">work for these people?</font>
你是说你叔叔去为这些人工作了?

85
00:06:22,187 --> 00:06:24,417
<font color="gray">- Mmm-hmm.</font>
<font color="gray">- Well, surely we can get in touch with him.</font>
- 嗯哼  - 那, 我们当然可以联系上他了

86
00:06:24,507 --> 00:06:27,260
<font color="gray">Well, you can try telephoning,</font>
<font color="gray">but I doubt if you'll get any joy.</font>
是, 你可以试着打打电话, 但我怀疑你不会得到好结果

87
00:06:27,347 --> 00:06:29,622
<font color="gray">Oh, phone's in the hall and</font>
<font color="gray">the number's scribbled on the wall.</font>
哦, 电话就在大厅里, 号码写在墙上呢

88
00:06:29,707 --> 00:06:31,026
<font color="gray">Thank you.</font>
谢谢你

89
00:06:31,387 --> 00:06:32,706
<font color="gray">Hey. Don't go.</font>
嘿, 不要走

90
00:06:32,787 --> 00:06:34,982
<font color="gray">I don't often get the chance of</font>
<font color="gray">photographing a real model.</font>
我并不是总有机会能给一个真正的模特拍照片

91
00:06:35,067 --> 00:06:36,056
<font color="gray">Oh, all right.</font>
噢, 好吧

92
00:06:36,147 --> 00:06:37,546
<font color="gray">Come on. Let's get you fixed up with some gear!</font>
快来, 我们来给你拍几张好看的(?)

93
00:06:37,707 --> 00:06:41,256
<font color="gray">WOMAN: <i>International Electromatic Company.</i></font>
<font color="gray"><i>State your business.</i></font>
国际电气自动化公司. 请陈述你的目的

94
00:06:41,347 --> 00:06:45,101
<font color="gray">I would like, please,</font>
<font color="gray">to speak with Professor Watkins.</font>
我想要, 请帮忙, 与 Watkins 教授通话

95
00:06:46,027 --> 00:06:47,380
<font color="gray"><i>One moment.</i></font>
等一下

96
00:06:48,907 --> 00:06:51,785
<font color="gray"><i>- Party not available.</i></font>
<font color="gray">- Oh, yes. You see, but this is very important.</font>
- 当事人不在  - 噢, 这样. 你看, 这事非常重要

97
00:06:51,867 --> 00:06:52,982
<font color="gray"><i>Party not available.</i></font>
当事人不在

98
00:06:53,067 --> 00:06:56,139
<font color="gray">- Yes, but I must speak with him.</font>
<font color="gray"><i>- Party not available.</i></font>
- 是的, 但我必须同他通话  - 当事人不在

99
00:06:56,227 --> 00:06:58,980
<font color="gray"><i>- Party not available.</i></font>
<font color="gray">- But this is an automatic answering device!</font>
- 当事人不在  - 这是一台自动应答设备!

100
00:06:59,067 --> 00:07:01,262
<font color="gray">Ah, shut up, you stupid machine!</font>
啊, 闭嘴, 你个愚蠢的机器!

101
00:07:01,347 --> 00:07:04,020
<font color="gray">- So, now what?</font>
<font color="gray">- There's only one thing for it!</font>
- 那, 现在怎办?   - 就只有一件事可做了!

102
00:07:04,107 --> 00:07:06,496
<font color="gray">We'll have to go there ourselves.</font>
我们只能自己去那里

103
00:07:07,587 --> 00:07:10,624
<font color="gray">Okay, that's fabulous, just keep it like that.</font>
好, 那样很漂亮, 就这样保持住

104
00:07:11,347 --> 00:07:13,178
<font color="gray">Great. Any luck?</font>
很好. 运气如何?

105
00:07:13,267 --> 00:07:16,464
<font color="gray">No, it was a stupid simple-minded</font>
<font color="gray">computer answering service.</font>
不怎样, 只有一个愚蠢而死脑筋的电脑应答服务

106
00:07:16,547 --> 00:07:17,662
<font color="gray">Well, what do we do now?</font>
那, 我们现在怎么做?

107
00:07:17,747 --> 00:07:19,419
<font color="gray">Well, Jamie and I are going to this place.</font>
<font color="gray">Come on, Zoe.</font>
Jamie 和我打算去那个地方. 来吧, Zoe

108
00:07:19,507 --> 00:07:21,782
<font color="gray">Oh, no, thanks. I think I'll stay here.</font>
<font color="gray">It's great fun.</font>
哦, 不, 谢谢. 我想我还是待在这里, 这很有意思

109
00:07:21,867 --> 00:07:23,744
<font color="gray">You look like a chicken with all those feathers on!</font>
你穿上那些衣服就像一只小鸡!

110
00:07:23,827 --> 00:07:25,783
<font color="gray">Well, come on, Jamie. Oh, the address?</font>
好, 来吧, Jamie. 哦, 地址有吗?

111
00:07:25,867 --> 00:07:27,983
<font color="gray">- Oh, that's scribbled on the wall, too.</font>
<font color="gray">- DOCTOR: Oh, thank you.</font>
- 哦, 也在墙上写着呢  - 哦, 谢谢你

112
00:07:28,067 --> 00:07:30,137
<font color="gray">Do you not write anything down on paper at all?</font>
你是什么都不写在纸上吗?

113
00:07:30,227 --> 00:07:31,819
<font color="gray">Well, I'd only lose it if I did.</font>
要是我写在纸上的话, 只会把它弄丢

114
00:07:31,907 --> 00:07:35,024
<font color="gray">Writing on a wall is much safer.</font>
<font color="gray">You can't lose a wall, can you?</font>
写在墙上安全多了. 你不可能弄丢一堵墙, 是吧?

115
00:07:35,107 --> 00:07:36,096
<font color="gray">No.</font>
不能

116
00:08:22,147 --> 00:08:24,183
<font color="gray">HQ are checking now. Where are they?</font>
总部在检查了, 他们在哪儿?

117
00:08:24,267 --> 00:08:26,303
<font color="gray">Gone round the back, down the side alley.</font>
从后面绕过去了, 在旁边那个小巷里

118
00:08:26,387 --> 00:08:28,901
<font color="gray">It's a dead end, isn't it?</font>
<font color="gray">So they've got to come out this way!</font>
那是条死路, 对吧. 所以他们还是会从这条路出来!

119
00:08:28,987 --> 00:08:30,500
<font color="gray">If they come out.</font>
那得假设他们会出来

120
00:09:06,367 --> 00:09:08,597
<font color="gray">Come and sit down, gentlemen.</font>
过来坐下, 先生们

121
00:09:09,767 --> 00:09:11,359
<font color="gray">DOCTOR: Thank you.</font>
谢谢你

122
00:09:11,447 --> 00:09:14,942
<font color="gray">- You can go, Packer.  - Yes, sir.</font>
- 你可以走了, Packer  - 好的, 先生

123
00:09:19,967 --> 00:09:23,277
