啊, 是, Watkins 小姐

253
00:18:21,067 --> 00:18:23,103
<font color="gray">You're concerned about your uncle, aren't you?</font>
你在担心你的叔叔, 是吗?

254
00:18:23,187 --> 00:18:24,700
<font color="gray">I'd like to know where he is, yes.</font>
是, 我想知道他在那里

255
00:18:24,787 --> 00:18:28,496
<font color="gray">He's perfectly well, I assure you,</font>
