他非常好, 我可以向你保证, 虽然有一点...

256
00:18:29,627 --> 00:18:31,777
<font color="gray">uncooperative at the moment.</font>
目前来说不太合作

257
00:18:32,827 --> 00:18:35,261
<font color="gray">Your visit here is most opportune.</font>
你们来的时机相当好

258
00:18:35,947 --> 00:18:38,461
<font color="gray">I think that you can be very useful to me.</font>
我觉得你会对我非常有用

259
00:18:38,547 --> 00:18:40,299
