292
00:20:14,847 --> 00:20:16,075
<font color="gray">Yes, sir. Right here.</font>
有, 长官, 就在这里

293
00:20:16,167 --> 00:20:17,361
<font color="gray">- Is that a tank?  - Oh, no, no.</font>
- 那是一架塔克吗?   - 噢, 不, 不是

294
00:20:17,447 --> 00:20:18,641
<font color="gray">My units are on constant alert,</font>
我的部队会保持警惕

295
00:20:18,727 --> 00:20:20,066
<font color="gray">so should you find yourselves in any trouble,</font>
所以如果你们发现自己遇到任何麻烦

296
00:20:20,147 --> 00:20:23,005
<font color="gray">- you can just give us a call.</font>
<font color="gray">- Jolly good!</font>
- 就可以呼叫我们  - 太好了

297
00:20:23,087 --> 00:20:24,805
<font color="gray">- Here you are, sir.</font>
