307
00:20:50,987 --> 00:20:53,501
<font color="gray">Look, Jamie, sandwiches. I'm hungry.</font>
看, Jamie, 三明治. 我饿了

308
00:20:54,067 --> 00:20:55,898
<font color="gray">- Want one?  - Thank you.</font>
