是一种非常复杂的电路, 做得很小

325
00:21:41,027 --> 00:21:42,938
<font color="gray">What's so odd about that, then?</font>
那又有什么奇怪的?

326
00:21:43,027 --> 00:21:45,222
<font color="gray">It has nothing to do with the radio,</font>
