- 我把它叫做思维导师  - 哦, 是

489
00:29:50,847 --> 00:29:53,457
<font color="gray">The main difference from other teaching machines</font>
它与其它教学机器的主要差别

490
00:29:53,547 --> 00:29:56,886
<font color="gray">is that it's able to induce</font>
<font color="gray">emotional changes in the subject.</font>
就是它能诱导测试对象的情绪变化

491
00:29:56,967 --> 00:29:58,286
<font color="gray">JAMIE: Oh.</font>
噢

492
00:30:01,127 --> 00:30:03,357
<font color="gray">Our friend the Doctor is a resourceful man.</font>
我们的博士朋友是个足智多谋的人

493
00:30:03,447 --> 00:30:05,677
<font color="gray">No wonder our allies fear him.</font>
怪不得我们的盟友害怕他

494
00:30:05,807 --> 00:30:09,436
<font color="gray">- Our allies know him?</font>
<font color="gray">- Oh, yes, I was ordered to destroy him.</font>
- 我们的盟友知道他?   - 哦, 是的, 它们命令我消灭他

495
00:30:10,407 --> 00:30:13,717
<font color="gray">But first I must learn the secrets</font>
<font color="gray">of this extraordinary machine of his.</font>
但首先我必须掌握他那台非凡机器的秘密

496
00:30:13,807 --> 00:30:15,498
<font color="gray">If you're ordered to destroy him...</font>
如果它们的命令是要消灭他...

497
00:30:15,607 --> 00:30:18,198
<font color="gray">I don't take orders, Packer. I give them!</font>
我不接受命令, Packer, 我只下发命令!

498
00:30:20,367 --> 00:30:23,704
<font color="gray">Now, I think the time has come</font>
<font color="gray">to stop playing games with this Doctor!</font>
现在, 我觉得是时候停止与博士玩游戏了!

499
00:30:23,787 --> 00:30:24,915
<font color="gray">But what can we do?</font>
但我们能怎么做?

500
00:30:25,007 --> 00:30:27,896
<font color="gray">If, as you say, they have got Isobel</font>
<font color="gray">and your young friend,</font>
如果, 如你所说, 他们抓住了 Isobel 和你那年轻朋友

501
00:30:27,987 --> 00:30:29,381
<font color="gray">then we're entirely at their mercy.</font>
那我们就完全得看他们脸色了

502
00:30:29,467 --> 00:30:31,840
<font color="gray">No, no, not entirely.</font>
<font color="gray">There's my friend the Brigadier, remember?</font>
不, 不, 也不尽然. 还有我的准将朋友, 记得吗?

503
00:30:31,927 --> 00:30:33,585
<font color="gray">- Do you think he can help us?  - Possibly.</font>
- 你觉得他能帮助我们?   - 很可能

504
00:30:33,677 --> 00:30:35,497
<font color="gray">But quickly, tell me, what is Vaughn up to?</font>
但是快点, 告诉我, Vaughn 在图谋什么?

505
00:30:35,587 --> 00:30:38,998
<font color="gray">- What's he doing here?</font>
<font color="gray">- I know no more than you do.</font>
- 他在这里做些什么?   - 我知道得不比你多

506
00:30:39,087 --> 00:30:42,363
<font color="gray">He's a ruthless man, without morals or principles.</font>
他是个冷酷无情的人, 没有道德和原则

507
00:30:42,647 --> 00:30:48,040
<font color="gray">His object, I'm sure, is to get complete control</font>
<font color="gray">of the electronics industry of the world!</font>
他的目标, 我肯定, 是要全面控制整个世界的电子工业!

508
00:30:48,327 --> 00:30:49,680
<font color="gray">I wonder.</font>
我很好奇

509
00:30:49,767 --> 00:30:53,282
<font color="gray">I've a nasty feeling he's aiming</font>
<font color="gray">somewhat higher than that.</font>
我有一种不好的感觉, 他有某种比这更高的目标

510
00:30:56,247 --> 00:30:58,636
<font color="gray">Doctor, quick, somebody's coming.</font>
博士, 快, 有人来了

511
00:31:00,687 --> 00:31:02,518
<font color="gray">Don't bother, Doctor.</font>
别费事了, 博士

512
00:31:03,607 --> 00:31:04,926
<font color="gray">Allow me.</font>
让我来

513
00:31:07,887 --> 00:31:10,196
<font color="gray">Very ingenious. A simple magnet.</font>
很天才啊, 一块简单的磁铁

514
00:31:11,287 --> 00:31:12,959
<font color="gray">I congratulate you.</font>
我祝贺你

515
00:31:13,927 --> 00:31:15,360
<font color="gray">Oh, how kind.</font>
哦, 谢谢

516
00:31:16,087 --> 00:31:17,964
<font color="gray">However, you must surely realise</font>
但是, 你肯定明白

517
00:31:18,047 --> 00:31:21,119
<font color="gray">that it's forced me to consider</font>
<font color="gray">other methods to make you talk.</font>
这会逼我考虑其它方法来让你说话

518
00:31:21,207 --> 00:31:22,686
<font color="gray">What are you going to do?</font>
你打算做什么?

519
00:31:22,767 --> 00:31:25,440
<font color="gray">Your friend Zoe is due to arrive here shortly.</font>
你的朋友 Zoe 很快就该到了

520
00:31:25,527 --> 00:31:27,677
<font color="gray">So you have got her!</font>
<font color="gray">Listen, if you've harmed her in any...</font>
看来你抓了她! 听着, 如果你伤害她一根...

521
00:31:27,767 --> 00:31:31,282
<font color="gray">You may still be adolescent enough</font>
<font color="gray">to make idle threats, young man,</font>
你可以继续幼稚地做些空洞的威胁, 年轻人

522
00:31:31,367 --> 00:31:33,835
<font color="gray">but I can assure you, I am not.</font>
但我可以向你保证, 我就不会

523
00:31:37,327 --> 00:31:39,841
<font color="gray">I want your travel machine, Doctor.</font>
我要你的旅行机器, 博士

524
00:31:40,207 --> 00:31:43,324
<font color="gray">Otherwise, I shall hand your friend Zoe</font>
<font color="gray">over to Packer.</font>
否则, 我就会把你的朋友交给 Packer

525
00:31:43,407 --> 00:31:48,162
<font color="gray">It's a simple choice, and shouldn't take you</font>
<font color="gray">longer than an hour to consider.</font>
这是个简单的选择, 应该不需要超过一个小时来考虑

526
00:31:48,447 --> 00:31:50,358
<font color="gray">Take them away, Packer.</font>
把他们带走, Packer

527
00:31:52,607 --> 00:31:53,926
<font color="gray">- All right.  - All right.</font>
- 好啦  - 好啦

528
00:31:54,007 --> 00:31:56,441
<font color="gray">Leave them to me. I'll take them.</font>
把他们留给我, 我来处理

529
00:31:57,007 --> 00:32:00,443
<font color="gray">Now, Professor, I suggest you continue with your work.</font>
现在, 教授, 我建议你继续你的工作

530
00:32:06,007 --> 00:32:09,044
<font color="gray">Oh, dear. You know, Jamie,</font>
<font color="gray">I've always been rather scared of lifts.</font>
噢, 天. 你知道吗, Jamie, 我一直都很害怕电梯

531
00:32:09,127 --> 00:32:10,242
<font color="gray">Why?</font>
为什么?

532
00:32:10,327 --> 00:32:12,204
<font color="gray">I never even like to start them.</font>
我甚至从不喜欢启动它们

533
00:32:12,287 --> 00:32:13,845
<font color="gray">You will have to push the button for me.</font>
你必须得替我按按钮了

534
00:32:13,927 --> 00:32:15,121
<font color="gray">Keep your mouth shut. Do as you're told.</font>
闭上你的嘴. 按吩咐的做

535
00:32:15,227 --> 00:32:17,351
<font color="gray">- Yes, Jamie. Do as you're told.</font>
<font color="gray">- Oh, yes...</font>
- 是的, Jamie, 按吩咐的做  - 哦, 好...

536
00:32:17,457 --> 00:32:18,598
<font color="gray">PACKER: Be quiet!</font>
哦, 好...   - 安静!

537
00:32:19,047 --> 00:32:23,003
<font color="gray">Packer! Mr Packer,</font>
<font color="gray">I obviously can't let you hurt Zoe,</font>
Packer! Packer 先生, 显然我不能让你伤害 Zoe

538
00:32:23,087 --> 00:32:26,003
<font color="gray">and so I'll have to tell you</font>
<font color="gray">all you want to know, now.</font>
所以我只得把你们想知道的都告诉你们

539
00:32:26,087 --> 00:32:27,315
<font color="gray">You mean you're willing to talk?</font>
你意思是你愿意说了?

540
00:32:27,407 --> 00:32:29,159
<font color="gray">Yes, I'm sure that Mr Vaughn would...</font>
是的, 我确信 Vaughn 先生会...

541
00:32:29,247 --> 00:32:31,681
<font color="gray">- Oh, there he is now...</font>
<font color="gray">- Quick, Doctor.</font>
- 哦, 他不来了吗...  - 快点, 博士

542
00:32:35,327 --> 00:32:36,316
<font color="gray">Your knife.</font>
你的刀

543
00:32:36,407 --> 00:32:38,045
<font color="gray">Your knife. Give me your knife.</font>
你的刀, 给我你的刀

544
00:32:38,127 --> 00:32:40,243
<font color="gray">- Why? What are you going to do?</font>
<font color="gray">- I'm going to try and break the circuit.</font>
- 为什么? 你打算做什么?   - 我要试试能不能破坏电路

545
00:32:40,327 --> 00:32:41,396
<font color="gray">What would that do?</font>
那又会怎样?

546
00:32:41,487 --> 00:32:44,206
<font color="gray">Well, it will either stop the lift</font>
<font color="gray">or send us out of control.</font>
唔, 要么会让电梯停掉, 要么我们会失控掉下去

547
00:32:44,287 --> 00:32:45,481
<font color="gray">But we're six floors up.</font>
但我们在六楼上啊

548
00:32:45,567 --> 00:32:49,116
<font color="gray">We'll have to take that risk.</font>
<font color="gray">Hold tight, here we go.</font>
我们必须担这个风险. 抓紧了, 我们走

549
00:32:49,207 --> 00:32:50,435
<font color="gray">(CLATTERING)</font>

550
00:32:50,727 --> 00:32:55,118
<font color="gray">- Why are you so gullible, Packer?</font>
<font color="gray">- Just wait till I get hold of them. I'll...</font>
- 你怎么这么容易受骗, Packer?   - 等我抓到他们, 我要...

551
00:32:55,207 --> 00:32:59,086
<font color="gray">You'll do nothing!</font>
<font color="gray">I want them in one piece.</font>
你什么也不要做. 我要他们安然无恙

552
00:33:00,187 --> 00:33:01,645
<font color="gray">There was a 50/50 chance, you know, Jamie.</font>
这里有 50对50 的几率, 知道吧, Jamie

553
00:33:01,787 --> 00:33:03,145
<font color="gray">Yes, but what good has it done us?</font>
哦, 但对我们有什么好处呢?

554
00:33:03,227 --> 00:33:04,626
<font color="gray">I mean, we're stuck here in this lift now.</font>
我是说, 我们困在这个电梯里了

555
00:33:04,707 --> 00:33:06,937
<font color="gray">No. No, it's the lift that's stuck,</font>
不, 不, 被困住的是电梯

556
00:33:07,027 --> 00:33:08,460
<font color="gray">not us. Look!</font>
而不是我们. 看!

557
00:33:10,027 --> 00:33:11,142
<font color="gray">Hey, where does that lead to?</font>
嘿, 那东西通到哪里?

558
00:33:11,227 --> 00:33:14,537
<font color="gray">Out into the lift shaft, I imagine.</font>
<font color="gray">Quickly, on me back.</font>
通到电梯井外面, 我估计. 快点, 到我后面去

559
00:33:14,627 --> 00:33:17,744
<font color="gray">You know something?</font>
<font color="gray">You're a clever wee chappie!</font>
你知道吗? 你是个聪明的家伙!

560
00:33:18,947 --> 00:33:20,062
<font color="gray">(GRUNTING)</font>

561
00:33:20,827 --> 00:33:21,816
<font color="gray">(SIGHING)</font>

562
00:33:26,227 --> 00:33:27,865
<font color="gray">Thank you, Jamie.</font>
谢谢你, Jamie

563
00:33:28,707 --> 00:33:30,106
<font color="gray">Oh, my word!</font>
哦, 老天

564
00:33:30,827 --> 00:33:33,136
<font color="gray">Well, that's a long way up, isn't it?</font>
啊, 上去好远的路啊, 是不?

565
00:33:33,227 --> 00:33:36,424
<font color="gray">Oh, well, we better get cracking</font>
<font color="gray">before they realise what's happened, eh?</font>
哦, 我们最好快点爬, 一会儿他们就发现了

566
00:33:36,507 --> 00:33:38,737
<font color="gray">- Perhaps I'd better shut this.</font>
<font color="gray">- Aye.</font>
- 也许我最好关上这个  - 是啊

567
00:33:39,507 --> 00:33:40,496
<font color="gray">(DOCTOR GRUNTS)</font>

568
00:33:41,507 --> 00:33:44,067
<font color="gray">Hey, Doctor, I've just been thinking.</font>
嘿, 博士, 我刚才在想

569
00:33:44,147 --> 00:33:47,742
<font color="gray">What happens if they get the lift going</font>
<font color="gray">before we get to the top?</font>
我们到达顶楼之前, 如果他们开动了电梯会怎么样?

570
00:33:47,827 --> 00:33:49,465
<font color="gray">- Oh, that's simple.  - What?</font>
- 哦, 那很简单  - 怎样?

571
00:33:49,547 --> 00:33:52,744
<font color="gray">- We get squashed.</font>
<font color="gray">- Oh. What! Well, come on!</font>
- 我们会被撞死  - 噢, 什么! 那, 赶紧啊!

572
00:33:54,827 --> 00:33:56,021
<font color="gray">Right!</font>
对了

573
00:33:56,187 --> 00:33:58,655
<font color="gray">They've switched over the circuits.</font>
<font color="gray">The lift's working!</font>
他们换了电路板, 电梯可以工作了!

574
00:33:58,747 --> 00:34:01,022
<font color="gray">How splendid. Bring it up here.</font>
很棒! 开到这里来吧

575
00:34:02,907 --> 00:34:04,898
<font color="gray">Bring it up to the sixth floor.</font>
把它开到六楼

576
00:34:05,247 --> 00:34:06,236
<font color="gray">(CLANGING)</font>

577
00:34:07,167 --> 00:34:09,556
<font color="gray">Hey, that's not what I think it is, is it?</font>
嘿, 那不是我想的那样, 是吗?

578
00:34:09,647 --> 00:34:12,161
<font color="gray">I'm very much afraid it is. Come on!</font>
恐怕是的, 快点!

579
00:34:20,807 --> 00:34:23,765
<font color="gray">- We'll never make it!</font>
<font color="gray">- Yes, we will! Come on!</font>
- 我们到不了了  - 能, 我们可以的. 快点!

580
00:34:25,687 --> 00:34:26,836
<font color="gray">(LIFT CLATTERS)</font>

581
00:34:27,447 --> 00:34:29,039
<font color="gray">What's happened?</font>
发生了什么?

582
00:34:30,047 --> 00:34:33,278
<font color="gray">It's stopped! They must be checking.</font>
它停掉了. 他们肯定在检查

583
00:34:34,007 --> 00:34:36,979
<font color="gray">Come on, they may guess where we are</font>
<font color="gray">and come after us.</font>
快点, 他们可能在猜我们在哪儿, 会来追我们

584
00:34:37,047 --> 00:34:38,003
<font color="gray">The engineer's certain...</font>
工程人员很肯定...

585
00:34:38,087 --> 00:34:40,562
<font color="gray">- The shaft terminates in the roof, doesn't it, Packer?</font>
<font color="gray">- Yes, sir.</font>
- 这个竖井通到顶楼, 是吧, Packer?   - 是的, 先生

586
00:34:40,647 --> 00:34:44,200
<font color="gray">- Why didn't you think of that?</font>
<font color="gray">- I'll get them!</font>
- 你怎么没想到这个?  - 我去抓他们!

587
00:34:44,307 --> 00:34:46,757
<font color="gray">Call me when you do, Packer.</font>
<font color="gray">I'll be in my office.</font>
抓到了就叫我, Packer. 我就在我的办公室等

588
00:34:47,147 --> 00:34:51,380
<font color="gray">And please don't fail this time,</font>
<font color="gray">there's a good fellow.</font>
这次请不要失败了, 那里面有个好家伙

589
00:34:54,107 --> 00:34:55,859
<font color="gray">They've started it again!</font>
他们又开动了

590
00:34:58,267 --> 00:35:00,019
<font color="gray">Hurry, Jamie! Hurry!</font>
快点, Jamie! 快!

591
00:35:13,467 --> 00:35:16,186
<font color="gray">- Come on, Jamie.  - Wait a minute, Doctor.</font>
- 跟上, Jamie  - 等一下, 博士

592
00:35:16,587 --> 00:35:18,623
<font color="gray">No, come on. Let's see where we are.</font>
不, 快点. 我们来看看我们在哪儿?

593
00:35:26,547 --> 00:35:28,458
<font color="gray">- Now where?  - Down there.</font>
- 现在去哪儿?   - 下去那边

594
00:35:29,387 --> 00:35:30,820
<font color="gray">JAMIE: Oh, no!</font>
噢, 不是吧!

595
00:35:31,227 --> 00:35:34,105
<font color="gray">Well, we can't go down the lift again, can we?</font>
我们不能再搭电梯下去了, 对不?

596
00:35:34,187 --> 00:35:37,384
<font color="gray">Hello. There's a fire escape. Come on.</font>
哈罗, 这里有个消防出口. 快来

597
00:35:39,907 --> 00:35:42,296
<font color="gray">Oh, Packer, you do disappoint me.</font>
噢, Packer. 你真让我失望

598
00:35:42,947 --> 00:35:44,380
<font color="gray">They must have got down the fire escape, sir.</font>
他们肯定沿着消防通道下去了, 先生

599
00:35:44,467 --> 00:35:47,823
<font color="gray">And, of course, you didn't think</font>
<font color="gray">to have a guard on that!</font>
而且, 你当然没有想到派一个人守在那里!

600
00:35:47,907 --> 00:35:50,262
<font color="gray">- Well, normally...</font>
<font color="gray">- You're a stupid incompetent!</font>
- 只是, 通常...  - 你真是愚蠢无能!

601
00:35:50,347 --> 00:35:51,939
<font color="gray">I want that Doctor!</font>
我要那位博士!

602
00:35:52,027 --> 00:35:55,576
<font color="gray">Put the whole compound on alert!</font>
<font color="gray">Have every available guard on the job!</font>
整个园区发布告警! 把所有警卫都派到这个事情上!

603
00:35:55,667 --> 00:35:58,386
<font color="gray">Find him, Packer! Find him!</font>
找到他, Packer! 找到他!

604
00:36:06,867 --> 00:36:08,346
<font color="gray">(ALARM BLARING)</font>

605
00:36:21,067 --> 00:36:22,217
<font color="gray">- GUARD: You two! Over here!</font>
你们俩, 过来!

606
00:36:22,307 --> 00:36:25,424
<font color="gray">Get those two girls over to</font>
<font color="gray">the main administration building! Move!</font>
把这两个女孩儿带到主行政大楼去! 走!

607
00:36:25,507 --> 00:36:28,624
<font color="gray">- Zoe and Isobel.</font>
<font color="gray">- Wait. We'll follow in a few moments.</font>
- 是 Zoe 和 Isobel  - 等等,  我们一会儿再跟上

608
00:36:46,407 --> 00:36:49,524
<font color="gray">Take them inside. Central block, tenth floor.</font>
带她们进去. 中央区域, 10楼

609
00:37:03,647 --> 00:37:05,558
<font color="gray">(ROTORS WHIRRING)</font>

610
00:37:13,287 --> 00:37:15,517
<font color="gray">Could be the Brigadier's lot.</font>
<font color="gray">Call them up for help.</font>
可能是准将的人. 请求他们帮助

611
00:37:15,607 --> 00:37:18,440
<font color="gray">No, no, not yet.</font>
<font color="gray">We've got to rescue the girls first.</font>
不, 不, 先不要. 我们得先把这两姑娘救出来

612
00:37:18,527 --> 00:37:21,041
<font color="gray">Tenth floor, central block. Come on.</font>
10楼, 中央区域. 快点

613
00:37:25,647 --> 00:37:28,605
<font color="gray">There's a lot of unusual activity, sir.</font>
<font color="gray">Guards everywhere.</font>
有很多异常活动, 长官. 到处都是警卫

614
00:37:28,687 --> 00:37:31,247
<font color="gray">It looks like some sort of emergency.</font>
看起来像是某种紧急状况

615
00:37:31,327 --> 00:37:33,397
<font color="gray">BRIGADIER: <i>Any sign of the Doctor and the boy?</i></font>
有博士和那个男孩儿的踪迹吗?

616
00:37:33,487 --> 00:37:35,239
<font color="gray">No, sir. None at all.</font>
没有, 长官. 完全没有

617
00:37:35,887 --> 00:37:38,845
<font color="gray"><i>Right,Jimmy. Get out of the area and stand by.</i></font>
好, Jimmy. 撤离那个区域, 待命

618
00:37:38,927 --> 00:37:40,679
<font color="gray">Right, sir. Will do.</font>
收到, 长官. 马上执行

619
00:37:47,707 --> 00:37:50,346
<font color="gray">- All units, please, Sergeant.</font>
<font color="gray">- Yes, sir.</font>
- 请接所有小组, 中士  - 是, 长官

620
00:37:51,147 --> 00:37:52,626
<font color="gray">Go ahead, sir.</font>
开始吧, 长官

621
00:37:54,907 --> 00:37:57,740
<font color="gray">This is the Brigadier. All units, stand by.</font>
我是准将. 所有小组, 准备

622
00:37:58,427 --> 00:38:00,816
<font color="gray">Full penetration of red sector imminent.</font>
即将全面突入红区

623
00:38:01,287 --> 00:38:02,515
<font color="gray">Hey, Zoe.</font>
嘿, Zoe

624
00:38:03,287 --> 00:38:04,606
<font color="gray">Zoe, look!</font>
Zoe, 看!

625
00:38:05,767 --> 00:38:07,598
<font color="gray">- Doctor!  - Jamie!</font>
- 博士!   - Jamie!

626
00:38:08,487 --> 00:38:09,602
<font color="gray">Yes, Doctor, come in.</font>
是的, 博士, 进来

627
00:38:09,687 --> 00:38:13,965
<font color="gray"><i>Brigadier, I think we shall require</i></font>
<font color="gray"><i>a little assistance in a few moments.</i></font>
准将, 我想再过一小会儿我们需要一点援助

628
00:38:14,047 --> 00:38:15,196
<font color="gray">Are you in trouble?</font>
你们遇到麻烦了?

629
00:38:15,287 --> 00:38:19,565
<font color="gray"><i>No, but we shall need help.</i></font>
<font color="gray"><i>You have a helicopter in the area?</i></font>
还没有, 但我们需要帮助. 你在这个区域有直升机吧?

630
00:38:19,647 --> 00:38:20,762
<font color="gray">Yes.</font>
是的

631
00:38:20,967 --> 00:38:24,198
<font color="gray"><i>I wonder, have they a rope ladder on board?</i></font>
我在想, 他们那里有绳梯吗?

632
00:38:24,287 --> 00:38:26,676
<font color="gray">Yes, I'm pretty sure they have. Where are you?</font>
是的, 我非常肯定他们有. 你们在哪里?

633
00:38:26,767 --> 00:38:29,600
<font color="gray"><i>We're just going up to the roof</i></font>
<font color="gray"><i>of the main building.</i></font>
我们正要上到主楼的楼顶去

634
00:38:29,687 --> 00:38:33,919
<font color="gray"><i>That is the central block on the north side.</i></font>
主楼在北边的中央区域

635
00:38:34,447 --> 00:38:38,725
<font color="gray"><i>That should give your helicopter cover</i></font>
<font color="gray"><i>should there be any ground fire.</i></font>
那个位置可以给直升机一点遮挡, 说不准地面会有火力袭击

636
00:38:38,887 --> 00:38:40,923
<font color="gray"><i>- Have you got that?</i></font>
<font color="gray">- Yes, I've got that.</font>
- 你收到了吗?   - 是的, 我收到了

637
00:38:41,007 --> 00:38:42,201
<font color="gray">Over and out.</font>
完毕, 挂断

638
00:40:06,327 --> 00:40:08,397
<font color="gray">You were lucky, dead lucky.</font>
你们很幸运, 非常幸运

639
00:40:08,567 --> 00:40:11,957
<font color="gray">He said it would be</font>
<font color="gray">a simple rescue operation. Simple.</font>
他说将是一个简单的营救行动. 简单

640
00:40:12,047 --> 00:40:13,162
<font color="gray">But what about my uncle?</font>
但我的叔叔怎么办?

641
00:40:13,247 --> 00:40:15,602
<font color="gray">- They've still got him prisoner.</font>
<font color="gray">- Don't worry, Miss Watkins.</font>
- 他还处于他们的监禁之下  - 别担心, Watkins 小姐

642
00:40:15,687 --> 00:40:18,724
<font color="gray">As soon as we return to base,</font>
<font color="gray">I'm going to raise hell and get some action.</font>
等我们一回到基地, 我就增派人手, 展开一些行动

643
00:40:18,807 --> 00:40:20,126
<font color="gray">You think they'll listen to you now?</font>
你觉得他们现在会听你的了?

644
00:40:20,207 --> 00:40:24,644
<font color="gray">No one, not even Tobias Vaughn, can go as far</font>
<font color="gray">as trying to shoot down one of my helicopters.</font>
没人能够猖狂到想把我的直升飞机打下来, 就算 Tobias Vaughn 也不行

645
00:40:24,727 --> 00:40:28,197
<font color="gray">Oh, I wish I'd had my camera.</font>
<font color="gray">I could have got a fortune for those pictures.</font>
噢, 我期望我带了相机来, 本来有幸可以拍到一些照片的

646
00:40:28,287 --> 00:40:29,515
<font color="gray">Yes, it was a pity.</font>
是的, 真遗憾

647
00:40:29,607 --> 00:40:32,075
<font color="gray">That would have clinched it</font>
<font color="gray">as far as the Ministry are concerned, sir.</font>
那样的话就可以在国防部那里实捶他们了, 长官

648
00:40:32,167 --> 00:40:35,364
<font color="gray">Don't worry, Jimmy. Billy Rutlidge</font>
<font color="gray">will have to take some action now.</font>
别担心, Jimmy. Billy Rutlidge 现在必须采取些行动了

649
00:40:35,507 --> 00:40:37,177
<font color="gray">Why am I being taken back to London?</font>
为什么把我带回伦敦?

650
00:40:37,267 --> 00:40:39,940
<font color="gray">What about my niece? What's happened to Isobel?</font>
我的侄女怎么样了? Isobel 她发生了什么?

651
00:40:40,027 --> 00:40:41,699
<font color="gray">I tell you, she's perfectly safe.</font>
我告诉你, 她相当安全

652
00:40:41,787 --> 00:40:43,778
<font color="gray">I want to see her!</font>
我想要见她!

653
00:40:43,867 --> 00:40:45,300
<font color="gray">So you shall.</font>
那你会的

654
00:40:45,587 --> 00:40:48,021
<font color="gray">When you've finished working on your machine.</font>
只要你先完成那台机器

655
00:40:48,627 --> 00:40:51,619
<font color="gray">Do as I ask and you shall both go free.</font>
按我要求的做, 你们俩都可以得到自由

656
00:40:53,267 --> 00:40:56,304
<font color="gray">You don't even expect me to believe you, do you?</font>
你没指望我会相信你吧, 是吗

657
00:40:56,387 --> 00:40:58,696
<font color="gray">Well, you've very little choice.</font>
只是, 你的选择很少

658
00:41:01,147 --> 00:41:02,899
<font color="gray">Now, we're going back to London.</font>
现在, 我们要回到伦敦

659
00:41:02,987 --> 00:41:06,582
<font color="gray">There you will work on your machine</font>
<font color="gray">to my specifications.</font>
你在那里要按我定的规格做出那台机器

660
00:41:07,787 --> 00:41:10,426
<font color="gray">You will have 24 hours to complete it.</font>
你有24小时来完成这项任务

661
00:41:10,907 --> 00:41:14,183
<font color="gray">Only if you haven't finished your work by that time</font>
如果你到那时还没有完成你的工作

662
00:41:14,347 --> 00:41:17,464
<font color="gray">would you have cause to worry about your niece.</font>
你才有理由担心你的侄女

663
00:41:19,067 --> 00:41:21,820
<font color="gray">- BRIGADIER: Mean anything to you, Doctor?</font>
<font color="gray">- Possibly.</font>
- 让你想起什么吗, 博士?   - 可能吧

664
00:41:22,347 --> 00:41:25,180
<font color="gray">How long ago were these objects first sighted?</font>
第一次看见这些东西是在多久以前?

665
00:41:25,267 --> 00:41:28,100
<font color="gray">Reports have been drifting in</font>
<font color="gray">for well over a year now.</font>
一年多以前就陆续有报告送过来

666
00:41:28,187 --> 00:41:31,304
<font color="gray">We sent up fighter planes to investigate,</font>
<font color="gray">but nothing ever came of it.</font>
我们派了战斗机去调查, 但没有任何结果

667
00:41:31,387 --> 00:41:32,743
<font color="gray">The odd thing about these sightings is</font>
这些目击事件比较奇怪的地方是

668
00:41:32,827 --> 00:41:36,818
<font color="gray">that they usually seem to disappear</font>
<font color="gray">somewhere over southeast England.</font>
它们似乎通常都消失在英格兰的东南部某处

669
00:41:36,907 --> 00:41:40,183
<font color="gray">But isn't that where all those factories</font>
<font color="gray">and laboratories of Vaughn's are?</font>
但那不就是 Vaughn 的工厂和实验室所在的地方吗?

670
00:41:40,267 --> 00:41:41,197
<font color="gray">Exactly.</font>
的确

671
00:41:41,667 --> 00:41:44,364
<font color="gray">Well, obviously they bring these things,</font>
<font color="gray">whatever they are..</font>
那, 显然是他们把这些东西, 不管它们是什么...

672
00:41:44,447 --> 00:41:46,983
<font color="gray">up from the factory in the country</font>
<font color="gray">to the London premises.</font>
从乡村的工厂带到了伦敦市区

673
00:41:47,067 --> 00:41:48,500
<font color="gray">That's where we're going to find the answer.</font>
那就是我们要去寻找答案的地方

674
00:41:48,587 --> 00:41:50,464
<font color="gray">You mean go back to Vaughn's place?</font>
你是说回到 Vaughn 的地盘去?

675
00:41:50,547 --> 00:41:53,459
<font color="gray">I don't think that's wise, Doctor.</font>
<font color="gray">You've been lucky so far.</font>
我觉得那样并不明智, 博士. 你们目前已经够幸运的了

676
00:41:53,547 --> 00:41:55,185
<font color="gray">Aye, if you think I'm going back inside there...</font>
是. 如果你觉得我打算回到那里面去...

677
00:41:55,267 --> 00:41:56,985
<font color="gray">Jamie, we have to find what is inside these crates.</font>
Jamie, 我们必须搞明白那些板条箱里面是什么

678
00:41:57,067 --> 00:42:01,538
<font color="gray">Brigadier, have you got a map,</font>
<font color="gray">including the London premises?</font>
准将, 你有地图吗, 包含伦敦市区的?

679
00:42:01,627 --> 00:42:04,699
<font color="gray">- Yes, yes, I think so. Sergeant Walters!</font>
<font color="gray">- Sir?</font>
- 有,  有, 我想是有. Walters 中士!  - 长官!

680
00:43:01,507 --> 00:43:04,419
<font color="gray">- Jamie, I'm afraid I was right!  - Eh?</font>
- Jamie, 恐怕我说对了  - 呃?

